ZH: 这只兔子很可爱。
EN: This rabbit is very cute.

ZH: 兔子在草地上跳来跳去。
EN: The rabbit is hopping around in the grass.

ZH: 小兔子在田野里玩耍。
EN: The little rabbit is playing in the field.

ZH: 玩具兔子造型很逼真。
EN: The toy rabbit has a very realistic design.

ZH: 兔子喜欢吃胡萝卜。
EN: Rabbits like to eat carrots.

ZH: 在春天，兔子会生出胡须。
EN: In the spring, rabbits grow whiskers.

ZH: 我的家里有一只兔子作为宠物。
EN: I have a rabbit as a pet in my home.

ZH: 兔子是一个温顺的动物。
EN: Rabbits are gentle animals.

ZH: 他的宠物兔子叫小白。
EN: His pet rabbit is named Snowball.

ZH: 公园里有许多野生的兔子。
EN: There are many wild rabbits in the park.

ZH: 兔子的耳朵很长。
EN: Rabbits have long ears.

ZH: 孩子们在追逐小兔子。
EN: The children are chasing after the baby rabbit.

ZH: 兔子的尾巴是软软的。
EN: Rabbit's tail is fluffy.

ZH: 这只兔子喜欢晒太阳。
EN: This rabbit likes to sunbathe.

ZH: 兔子在青草中找到了一个洞穴。
EN: The rabbit found a burrow in the green grass.

ZH: 兔子总是跳跃的姿态。
EN: Rabbits always have a hopping manner.

ZH: 兔子的尾巴有时候会短短的。
EN: Sometimes, rabbits have short tails.

ZH: 我的妹妹很喜欢兔子。
EN: My little sister really likes rabbits.

ZH: 兔子是地球上最快的动物之一。
EN: Rabbits are one of the fastest animals on Earth.

ZH: 兔子可以代表机智和敏捷。
EN: Rabbits can symbolize wit and agility.
